Key Improvements v5.8:
- Farmer Balance: "勤劳积德" passive (+2 merit if labor ≥5)
- Farmer Vow Rewards: Simple +12, Difficult +20 (was 10/18)
- Merchant Vow Fix: "资施功德" requires 5 donations (was 7)
- Monk Protect Specialization: cost 1, merit +4, blessing +2
- Mutual Aid Action: new 6th action type
- Resource Token Cards: 45 printable tokens (1/2/5 × gold/red/blue)
- Event Card Expansion: 20 universal + 16 profession-specific = 36 total

